## ER Diagram Legend

| Entity | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| **USER** | External | Firebase Authentication |
| **RECEIPT_WARRANTY** | Local (Room) | Main entity for receipts and warranties |
| **DELETED_ITEM** | Local (Room) | Tracks deleted items for sync |
| **FIRESTORE_RECEIPT** | Cloud (Firestore) | Cloud storage of receipts/warranties |
| **FIRESTORE_PROFILE** | Cloud (Firestore) | User profile data |
| **FIRESTORE_SYNC** | Cloud (Firestore) | Sync metadata |
| **DRIVE_FILE** | External | Google Drive image storage |

### Relationships

- **1:N** - One User has Many ReceiptWarranty items
- **1:N** - One User has Many DeletedItem records
- **0..1:1** - ReceiptWarranty optionally has one DriveFile (image)
- **1:1** - User has one FirestoreProfile
- **1:1** - User has one FirestoreSync metadata
- **sync** - ReceiptWarranty syncs to FirestoreReceipt
